USE ROLE SECURITYADMIN;
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON DATABASE STG_KONTROLSYS_NO TO ROLE SYSADMIN;
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON ALL SCHEMAS IN DATABASE STG_KONTROLSYS_NO TO ROLE SYSADMIN;
GRANT USAGE ON DATABASE STG_KONTROLSYS_NO TO ROLE DATA_LOADER;

GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON ALL SCHEMAS IN DATABASE STG_KONTROLSYS_NO TO ROLE DATA_LOADER;

GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON ALL TABLES IN SCHEMA STG_KONTROLSYS_NO.DBO TO ROLE DATA_LOADER;

GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON FUTURE TABLES IN SCHEMA STG_KONTROLSYS_NO.DBO TO ROLE DATA_LOADER;



